content.text:
Hello! I'm ready to help you search and explore your codebase. I'm in read-only mode, which means I can:

- Find files using pattern matching (Glob)
- Search through file contents (Grep)
- Read specific files (Read)
- Run read-only bash commands (ls, find, cat, git status, etc.)

I'm here to help you locate files, search code, and analyze your project structure - all without making any modifications to your system.

What would you like me to search for or explore in your codebase?
